{"tid":2385580,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"窮人唔好...?  烏干達媽「24年狂生44胎」","createTime":"2021-01-29T06:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T08:13:57.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9cd4f12a4144fb28e4d131c32e074aa763eb249e","tid":2385580,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T06:17:46.000Z","msg":"根據《鏡報》報導，現年42歲的烏干達媽媽娜芭坦姬（Mariam Nabatanzi），12歲那年結婚，嫁給了大她28歲的丈夫，婚後第一年先是產下一對雙胞胎，之後不斷過著懷孕生產日子，24年來至少懷孕16次，至今生下44個孩子，其中包含5對雙胞胎、4對三胞胎、5對四胞胎，只有2次只生一胎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/v41Vyh7yjBI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fv41Vyh7yjBI&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=ea4698c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/v41Vyh7yjBI</a><br />\n<br />\n娜芭坦姬發現自己比常人更容易受孕，日前赴醫院求助，才發現罹患罕見遺傳疾病，卵巢尺寸異常大且功能發達，可能在一個周期內，就能釋放出多顆卵子，致使受孕機會增加。醫師警告她別再生了，擔心她若服用避孕藥，恐對身體造成影響，40歲那年她決定將子宮摘除，以消除再度懷孕風險。<br />\n<br />\n娜芭坦姬生下的44個孩子中，有6人不幸夭折，僅剩38個孩子存活下來，因為家中人口眾多，致使家庭經濟陷入困境，一家人擠在4間狹窄房子，但床舖根本睡不下，有些孩子只能被迫睡在地上。<br />\n<br />\n但悲慘的是，娜芭坦姬5年前被丈夫拋棄，不得不獨自撫養這些孩子長大成人，她要求每個孩子都要學會做家事，其中23歲長子伊萬(Ivan Kibuka)更被迫輟學賺錢來分擔家計，但他並未因此埋怨母親，反而懂事地說：「媽媽被壓垮了，工作壓得她喘不過氣來，我們盡己所能幫助她，比如做飯和洗衣，但她仍然承擔著整個家庭的負擔，我很心疼她。」<br />\n<br />\n根據世界銀行統計，全球家庭平均孩子的生育數是2.4位，但在烏干達卻平均生育5.6位，這在非洲排名第二。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=889795\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D889795&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=68c9b695\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D889795&h=71e37e6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=889795</a>"},{"pid":"e9abeb44c608a8ceee29d4c7184e6875e825dcbe","tid":2385580,"uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T06:18:29.000Z","msg":"4對三胞胎、5對四胞胎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37bdb1ef632cf03d0d0eecadae5b04ac4922105","tid":2385580,"uid":165336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T06:18:36.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa993303635b2b546a9973be244b5dc735f4f7c6","tid":2385580,"uid":78243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T06:18:37.000Z","msg":"意外懷孕"},{"pid":"5cf35feb30a2d7e96a65be16379cf778071a55cf","tid":2385580,"uid":53122,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T06:19:51.000Z","msg":"所以窮人之所以窮<br />\n根本係自己做成<br />\n<br />\n你班傻閪仲走去捐宣明會幫佢哋"},{"pid":"912f1549653310529ba3cf90ad2b50e627587fda","tid":2385580,"uid":59283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T06:19:58.000Z","msg":"uganda forever"},{"pid":"48057ef9761d3f46a76a18bac60cd49d827529a9","tid":2385580,"uid":36435,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T06:20:45.000Z","msg":"然後ngo叫人捐錢俾佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a8b90635ae543bcffa40822fca3be593d2f078","tid":2385580,"uid":160964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T06:21:09.000Z","msg":"生左成村人出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"397a3dc9c75805c72df4883615487cece4b9532b","tid":2385580,"uid":6063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T06:21:42.000Z","msg":"咒胎9相圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31532519dfa35f697bbdac85d390522130acf961","tid":2385580,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"912f1549653310529ba3cf90ad2b50e627587fda","tid":2385580,"uid":59283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T06:19:58.000Z","msg":"uganda forever"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T06:22:16.000Z","msg":"U姦她 forever <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac